  "title": "Refactoring Cron-Driven Tasks Using FastAPI in Python 3.12+",
  "summary": "This guide provides a step-by-step approach to refactor cron-driven tasks using FastAPI, a modern, high-performance web framework for building APIs with Python 3.12+.",
